{
  "text": "The omptin structures were modelled on the basis of the crystal structures of Pla [CITATION_1] (PDB code 2x4m) with program Modeller 9v7 [CITATION_2] and analyzed visually with program VMD [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
